In 2008  Kenroy Home was purchased by its employees--a unique first in the lighting industry. Particular care is paid to hand applied polishing and painting  matched with the finest in glass and shade treatments. The company's chandeliers and ceiling lighting run the gamut of styles  from classical and traditional to contemporary and casual.
